---
title: "CC4ES | Connect"
description: "CC4ES Connect"
hero_title: "CONNECT"
hero_subtitle: "Network references for each of CC4ES Six Modules"
---

<%= partial 'partials/header' %>

<article class="grid-container">
  
  <div class="grid-x grid-margin-x">
    <div class="cell small-12 text-center">
      <h2>About CONNECT</h2>
      <p>CONNECT houses a compiled list of organizations in various sectors working on the sustainability causes or relevant to sustainaiblity, available for network mapping.  Such mapping is an integral part of collaboration coordination neccessary for collective shift as it provides converged comprehensive visions for any given projects.  
        
        CC4ES would like to attribute to Susan Korte of Providential Gardener who has been relentlessly compiling various lists, from which this list was created.
      </p>
    </div>

  <article class="grid-container">

  <div class="grid-x grid-margin-x grid-padding-x grid-margin-y">

    <% data.connect.connect_entries.each do |entry| %>
    <div class="entry-div cell small-12 medium-12">
      <div class="title-with-photo grid-x grid-margin-x grid-padding-y" style="padding:0;border:2px solid #cec6e6;">
        <h4 class="entry-title cell medium-12" style="text-align:center;margin:0;background:#cec6e6;width:100%;"><%= entry.name %></h4>
        <div class="entry-description cell medium-6 small-12">
          <%= markdown(entry.description) %>
          <% if entry.link %>
            <p class="entry-link"><a href="<%= entry.link %>">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
          <% end %>
        </div>
#        <div class="entry-modules cell medium-6 small-12" style="font-size:90%;">
#          <p><b>Relevant modules:</b></p>
#          <%= markdown(entry.modules) %>
#        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <% end %>

  </div>

</article>

<style>

  article .entry-description p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  article .entry-modules p {
    font-size: 1.0rem;
  }

</style>
